## 1. General Description and Disclaimer

- **Purpose of the App**  
  Cinematik is a watchlist and entertainment-tracking application. It allows its users to discover, search, and keep track of TV shows and movies. **Cinematik does not provide streaming services, and you cannot watch TV shows or movies directly within our App.** All references to titles, schedules, and availability are for informational purposes only.

- **No Liability for Missed or Unavailable Content**  
  We do not guarantee the availability, reliability, or accuracy of any information provided in the App, including (but not limited to) release dates, streaming availability, or show details. We rely, in part, on third-party services such as Trakt.tv and JustWatch for data. **Cinematik is not responsible or liable for any missed, inaccessible, removed content, or changes in showtimes, nor do we provide any refunds for subscription dissatisfaction related to this information.**

