## 2. Premium Subscriptions

- **Subscription Terms**  
  If you choose to subscribe to Cinematik Premium, payment is charged in advance through Apple’s in-app purchase system. Subscriptions may be available on a monthly or yearly basis.

- **Auto-Renewal**  
  Your subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. Your account will be charged for the renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.

- **Managing Your Subscription**  
  You can manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal at any time by going to your Account Settings on your device. **All payments are handled solely by Apple**; for any inquiries regarding refunds, please contact Apple Support.

